## Advanced: Adapting This Workflow

This workflow is flexible. Adapt it to your needs:

### For Smaller Features:
- Skip the long-term vision
- Focus on Steps 1-2-3-5-6
- Use AI for quick iteration, not strategic planning

### For Exploratory Projects:
- Generate many variations in Step 3
- Spend more time in stakeholder feedback (Step 5)
- Loop through strategic iteration multiple times
- Keep refinement (Step 6) lightweight

### For Complex Systems:
- Break into multiple sub-workflows
- Run Steps 1-5 for each major component
- Synthesize in a final integration phase
- Use AI to maintain consistency across components

### Without Figma Make:
- Use other AI tools (Midjourney, Galileo AI, etc.)
- Adjust Step 3 accordingly
- Core workflow structure remains the same

### When Ramping Up on Existing Projects:
- Use Guided Discovery Questions to understand current state
- Schedule interviews with existing team members
- Review existing designs and documentation
- Document gaps and assumptions
- Start with small iterations to build context

